tomorrow. Mark.

308
00:15:14.575 --> 00:15:15.967
Make sure you get
a good night's sleep.

309
00:15:15.991 --> 00:15:17.533
Ha! For sure!

310
00:15:28.616 --> 00:15:32.116
Okay. Son. bear with me...

311
00:15:32.158 --> 00:15:36.200
