awkward for both of us.

312
00:15:36.241 --> 00:15:37.616
You may have noticed

313
00:15:37.658 --> 00:15:41.116
that I'm not like
normal dads.

314
00:15:41.158 --> 00:15:44.033
Your mother and I think
it's time you knew the truth.

315
00:15:44.075 --> 00:15:46.908
We think you're old enough
for me to tell you

316
00:15:46.950 --> 00:15:49.533
where I really come from.

317
00:15:49.575 --> 00:15:51.575
Millions of miles from here.

318
00:15:51.616 --> 00:15:53.116
out in deep space.

319
00:15:53.158 --> 00:15:55.991
is the planet Viltrum...

320
00:15:56.033 --> 00:15:58.325
It's a cool blue oasis

321
00:15:58.366 --> 00:16:01.575
alone in a solar system
much like our own.

322
00:16:01.616 --> 00:16:03.408
I was born on this planet.

323
00:16:03.450 --> 00:16:06.283
Viltrumites
are very similar to humans.

324
00:16:06.325 --> 00:16:07.783
except we can fly.

325
00:16:07.825 --> 00:16:09.741
move at super speed.

326
00:16:09.783 --> 00:16:12.325
and possess great strength.

327
00:16:12.366 --> 00:16:13.950
When our people come of age.

328
00:16:13.991 --> 00:16:15.200
we leave Viltrum.

329
00:16:15.241 --> 00:16:17.325
and venture out
into the galaxy.

330
00:16:17.366 --> 00:16:20.575
