to Earth.

332
00:16:22.450 --> 00:16:24.741
and be its sole protector.

333
00:16:25.700 --> 00:16:26.991
That's when I met
your mother...

334
00:16:29.283 --> 00:16:32.158
and we eventually had you.

335
00:16:32.200 --> 00:16:36.491
I know this is a lot
to take in at one time.

336
00:16:36.533 --> 00:16:39.741
but you're
half Viltrumite. Son.

337
00:16:39.783 --> 00:16:41.658
and you're getting older.

338
00:16:41.700 --> 00:16:44.158
Things are gonna
start to change for you

339
00:16:44.200 --> 00:16:45.366
