349
00:17:06.533 --> 00:17:08.491
Do you understand?

350
00:17:11.616 --> 00:17:14.575
I'm gonna be able to fly?

351
00:17:14.616 --> 00:17:16.116
Yes. Son.

352
00:17:16.158 --> 00:17:19.783
you're gonna be able to fly...

353
00:17:19.825 --> 00:17:22.283
I'm gonna be able to fly.

354
00:17:26.325 --> 00:17:27.700
Whew.

355
00:17:27.741 --> 00:17:28.866
