358
00:17:31.491 --> 00:17:32.450
I'm gonna fly up.

359
00:17:32.491 --> 00:17:34.533
because I can fly.

360
00:17:35.366 --> 00:17:37.241
What if I can't yet?

361
00:17:37.283 --> 00:17:38.491
No. no. no. okay.

362
00:17:38.533 --> 00:17:40.366
Dad always said
it was like a reflex.

363
00:17:40.408 --> 00:17:42.283
so if I don't want to fall.
I won't.

364
00:17:42.325 --> 00:17:44.741
and even if I do.
maybe it won't even hurt.

365
00:17:44.783 --> 00:17:46.491
or maybe...

366
00:17:46.533 --> 00:17:48.491
Ah. screw it!

367
00:17:54.366 --> 00:17:56.325
Whoo-hoo!

368
00:17:58.908 --> 00:18:00.325
Whoa... oh. crap.

369
00:18:00.366 --> 00:18:01.366
Whoa! Oh. god...

370
00:18:05.325 --> 00:18:07.783
Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

371
00:18:09.075 --> 00:18:10.325
Ugh!

372
00:18:10.366 --> 00:18:12.283
No. no. no. no. no...

373
00:19:12.491 --> 00:19:13.450
Put some pants on.

374
00:19:13.491 --> 00:19:14.825
and let's get
in the sky. my boy.

375
00:19:20.783 --> 00:19:23.575
