to carry you forward.

393
00:20:09.866 --> 00:20:11.575
Okay. you don't want to fall.

394
00:20:11.616 --> 00:20:14.075
so you're gonna have trouble
relaxing.

395
00:20:14.116 --> 00:20:17.158
It's kind of like
peeing your pants on purpose.

396
00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:18.158
What?

397
00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:19.616
Peeing your pants on purpose.

398
00:20:19.658 --> 00:20:21.158
You know. you spend
your whole life

399
00:20:21.200 --> 00:20:22.950
trying not to pee your pants.

400
00:20:22.991 --> 00:20:26.533
so letting go.
peeing your pants on purpose.

401
00:20:26.575 --> 00:20:27.825
it's next to impossible.

402
00:20:27.866 --> 00:20:29.283
How how do you know this?

403
00:20:29.325 --> 00:20:30.991
Who would try that?

404
00:20:31.033 --> 00:20:33.533
You are far better at flying
than you should be.

405
00:20:33.575 --> 00:20:34.825
