with your shoulder.

425
00:21:19.616 --> 00:21:21.825
your hips.
and your legs as well.

426
00:21:21.866 --> 00:21:23.408
it'll be much more powerful.

427
00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:25.050
It'll take a while
to get the hang of it.

428
00:21:26.158 --> 00:21:26.991
Okay.

429
00:21:27.033 --> 00:21:28.366
Now. with us.

430
00:21:28.408 --> 00:21:31.575
