480
00:23:37.366 --> 00:23:38.908
Don't kick your ass again?

481
00:23:38.950 --> 00:23:40.825
Or what?
Are you threatening me?

482
00:23:40.866 --> 00:23:43.825
Or do you need a replay
of what happened last time. ass?

483
00:23:43.866 --> 00:23:45.491
Hit me.

484
00:23:46.533 --> 00:23:47.575
Go on.

485
00:23:47.616 --> 00:23:48.991
Hit me as hard as you can.

486
00:23:54.200 --> 00:23:55.408
Again.

487
00:23:58.408 --> 00:23:59.783
Again.

488
00:23:59.825 --> 00:24:01.450
Harder.

489
00:24:11.283 --> 00:24:12.783
Freak!

490
00:24:14.575 --> 00:24:16.991
