497
00:24:39.741 --> 00:24:41.991
Whoa...

498
00:24:42.033 --> 00:24:43.075
Dammit.

499
00:24:46.241 --> 00:24:47.533
Let's go!

500
00:24:55.700 --> 00:24:57.658
