519
00:26:05.866 --> 00:26:06.950
No...

520
00:26:06.991 --> 00:26:08.283
that sounds
willfully childish.

521
00:26:08.325 --> 00:26:09.158
What are you thinking?

522
00:26:09.200 --> 00:26:12.075
