523
00:26:13.366 --> 00:26:15.325
Let's get outta here.

524
00:26:18.200 --> 00:26:19.575
Whoa...

525
00:26:19.616 --> 00:26:20.616
Oof!

526
00:26:22.491 --> 00:26:23.700
Honestly.

527
00:26:23.741 --> 00:26:26.075
I think you might have
skipped a few steps. Mark.

528
00:26:27.158 --> 00:26:29.075
Seemed to work out just fine.

529
00:26:29.116 --> 00:26:30.575
It may not
look like much.

530
00:26:30.616 --> 00:26:32.783
but you did far more
damage down there

531
00:26:32.825 --> 00:26:34.158
than you needed to.

532
00:26:34.200 --> 00:26:35.575
I don't think
you're ready.

533
00:26:36.491 --> 00:26:37.408
Hit me.

534
00:26:37.450 --> 00:26:38.491
What?

535
00:26:38.533 --> 00:26:40.658
Hit me now.
Do it!

536
00:26:40.700 --> 00:26:42.075
I wasn't ready before.

537
00:26:42.116 --> 00:26:42.991
Now I am.

538
00:26:43.033 --> 00:26:44.241
I can take it.

539
00:26:44.283 --> 00:26:45.825
Come on!

540
00:26:45.866 --> 00:26:47.991
I'm not gonna hit you.

541
00:26:48.033 --> 00:26:49.217
You'd never
hit me before. okay?

542
00:26:49.241 --> 00:26:50.325
