I could take the pain.

544
00:26:51.991 --> 00:26:52.908
I'm strong.

545
00:26:52.950 --> 00:26:54.241
I know you are.

546
00:26:54.283 --> 00:26:55.283
No. you don't!

547
00:26:55.325 --> 00:26:56.991
