845
00:41:23.616 --> 00:41:24.575
Uh... Sam?

846
00:41:24.616 --> 00:41:25.575
What?

847
00:41:25.616 --> 00:41:26.616
Darkwing.

848
00:41:26.658 --> 00:41:28.158
Don't worry about him.

849
00:41:28.200 --> 00:41:29.783
He can't be everywhere.

850
00:41:34.075 --> 00:41:36.866
Luckily.
I don't have to be everywhere.

851
00:41:36.908 --> 00:41:39.783
Only where I'm needed.

852
00:42:02.950 --> 00:42:04.491
I know
what's in this building.

853
00:42:04.533 --> 00:42:05.950
