tomorrow.

857
00:42:17.950 --> 00:42:18.950
Wing Jet.

858
00:42:41.825 --> 00:42:43.408
Darkwing.

859
00:42:43.450 --> 00:42:45.116
why did you call us here?

860
00:42:45.158 --> 00:42:46.366
Me?

861
00:42:46.408 --> 00:42:48.116
So none of us
signaled the alert?

862
00:42:48.158 --> 00:42:49.950
Oh. god. what's going on?

863
00:42:49.991 --> 00:42:50.866
Is it bad?

864
00:42:53.533 --> 00:42:54.700
Huh?

865
00:43:09.950 --> 00:43:11.033
Omni-Man?

866
00:43:59.825 --> 00:44:01.116
- No!
- No!

867
00:44:05.450 --> 00:44:07.200
Why have you done this?

868
00:44:12.616 --> 00:44:13.616
Ah!

869
00:44:29.158 --> 00:44:30.825
Oh. no.

870
00:44:42.075 --> 00:44:43.283
Are you all right?

871
00:44:43.325 --> 00:44:44.575
I live.

872
00:44:44.616 --> 00:44:46.575
Someone must be
controlling him.

873
00:44:46.616 --> 00:44:48.575
He would never do this.

874
00:44:48.616 --> 00:44:51.575
Regardless. it's him or us.

875
00:44:52.700 --> 00:44:54.075
